           </td><td align="left"><span class="text"><a href="/upload/resize_cache/altasib.editortools/iblock/image001.gif" target="_blank" class="colorboxS"><img width="403" alt="image001.gif" src="/upload/medialibrary/cf5/image001.gif" height="335" title="image001.gif" border="0" class="donotresize"></a></span></td></tr>
